title: Detox from Disney
itunes:title: Detox from Disney
description:
Today on the show we opened up the phones to the parents that listen to the show, to see how they detox from Disney, after Charlamagne shared his story about being tired from taking his family to Disney world. Also Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Governor Kay Ivey and 25 white men who sign nation's most restrictive abortion bill and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
